and we meet again♪

60
00:04:06,306 --> 00:04:10,496
♪Piecing our memories desperately,
love takes us by surprise♪

61
00:04:11,252 --> 00:04:13,537
♪The you in the photo album♪

62
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:17,633
♪Are shining in the past like stars♪

63
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:22,789
♪You are in the light and shadow♪

64
00:04:22,924 --> 00:04:26,424
♪Melting all my fear away♪

65
00:04:26,805 --> 00:04:30,328
♪Those youthful memories
are healing enough♪

66
00:04:30,481 --> 00:04:32,576
♪That I become obsessed with them♪

67
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:37,600
Stop

68
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,920
