plant flowers in the garden.

85
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:33,920
And

86
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,120
I would help her

87
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,120
by causing a mess.

88
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,440
I worked so hard for you,

89
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,680
